data.description: Welcome to your spacious and inviting haven – the perfect home for your family's dreams! This stunning 5-bedroom, 2.5-bathroom residence offers a wealth of features tailored to accommodate the needs of a large family or family that needs space. As you step inside, you'll immediately be greeted by the warm and cohesive ambiance of the laminate flooring that flows seamlessly throughout the entire home. The expansive flex space downstairs invites endless possibilities – an ideal spot for a playroom, home office, or additional living area to suit your family's unique lifestyle. Upstairs, a versatile loft area awaits, providing the perfect space for family game nights or a cozy retreat. The grand primary bedroom is a true sanctuary, boasting ample room for a private office or sitting area, complemented by his and hers closets for convenient organization. Indulge in the luxurious en-suite bathroom within the primary bedroom, featuring a soaking tub and a separate shower – the ultimate relaxation haven after a busy day. With 5 bedrooms + flex spaces, there's ample space for everyone to enjoy their own private retreat. Situated on a generous corner .33-acre lot, this residence offers a fully fenced backyard, ensuring both privacy and safety for your loved ones. The expansive back patio beckons for family gatherings and entertaining, complete with a designated area for a firepit, creating the perfect ambiance for making lasting memories. The culinary enthusiast will appreciate the brand-new butcher-block counters in the kitchen, enhancing the functionality and style of this heart of the home. With a 3-car garage, parking and storage are never a concern, providing convenience and flexibility for a bustling family lifestyle. Conveniently located just minutes away from schools, shopping, dining, the Amazon hub, hospital, movie theatre, and I-4 access, this home perfectly balances suburban tranquility with urban convenience. Positioned between Orlando and New Smyrna Beach, you'll find yourself at the crossroads of city amenities and coastal escapes. This fully updated home, adorned with fresh interior paint, is ready to embrace your family's unique story. Don't miss the opportunity to call this residence your own – schedule a viewing today and step into the future of family living in Deltona!
